  "summary": "Dispatcher-side feature-touch orchestration surface. Owns the rabbit-feature-touch skill and three general-purpose helper skills (rabbit-feature-scope, rabbit-feature-new, rabbit-feature-audit) plus their backing scripts (resolve-scope.py, format-feature-context.py, new-feature.py). Spec lifecycle skills (rabbit-spec-create, rabbit-spec-update) are owned by rabbit-spec. Executor-side TDD machinery (dispatch-tdd-subagent.py, tdd-step.py) lives in tdd-subagent and is consumed via the cross-feature contract.",
